        "Bollinger La Côte Aux Enfants Rouge",
        "2015",
        "75cl",
        "8500.0",
        "3.0",
        "來自Bollinger傳奇單一園的稀世之作，2015年充沛的陽光孕育出這瓶深邃迷人的黑皮諾。杯中散發接骨木花、黑櫻桃與藍莓的濃郁果香，入口感受甘草與黑色水果的豐盈層次，胡椒與丁香的微妙辛香為其畫龍點睛，單寧絲滑而有力，餘韻悠長優雅。\n\nFrom Bollinger's legendary single vineyard, this rare Pinot Noir captivates with aromas of black cherry, blueberry and elderflower. Rich and velvety on the palate, with layers of dark fruit, liquorice and a whisper of spice — it's bold yet beautifully elegant, with a finish that lingers long after the last sip.",
        "https://www.12bouteilles.com/11006-large_default/champagne-bollinger-cote-aux-enfants-2016.jpg",
        "Sparkling"
    ],
    [
        "C",
        "",
        "France-法國",
        "Champagne-香檳",
        "Bollinger Special Cuvee",
        "N.V.",
        "75cl",
        "3000.0",
        "0.0",
        "Bollinger的靈魂之作，以超倍法定時間的窖藏與高比例珍稀Reserve Wine淬煉而成。烤蘋果、蜜餞與現烤布里歐麵包的暖香縈繞杯中，泡沫細膩如綢，口感醇厚飽滿，是一杯讓人瞬間讀懂 Bollinger 百年底蘊的經典香檳。\n\nThe soul of Bollinger in every sip. Aged far beyond the required minimum and blended with a rare high proportion of Reserve Wines spanning up to 15 years, this is no ordinary NV Champagne. Expect warm, inviting aromas of roasted apple, candied fruit and freshly baked brioche, with a silky mousse and a rich, structured palate that speaks effortlessly of Bollinger's century-old mastery.",
        "https://www.my9.com.tw/cdn/shop/products/K00201_1200x.png?v=1763539355",
        "Sparkling"
    ],
    [
        "C",
        "9410170.0",
        "France-法國",
        "Champagne-香檳",
        "Bollinger R.D. Extra Brut",
        "2008",
        "75cl",
        "18500.0",
        "1.0",
        "2008年份，當代最偉大的香檳年份之一，而R.D.則是其最極致的詮釋。晶透金黃的酒液中，杏仁糖、花蜜與烘烤麵包的香氣與佛手柑、石灰岩的礦感交相輝映，慕斯細緻如絲，柑橘的明亮、李子與蜜桃的豐潤在口中層層綻放，收尾以新鮮榛果與悠長鹹礦韻作結。時間與自然共同淬煉的稀世傑作。\n\nThe 2008 vintage is widely celebrated as one of the greatest Champagne years of the modern era — and Bollinger R.D. is its most breathtaking expression. Crystal-bright gold in the glass, it opens with enticing notes of marzipan, wild honey and toasted bread, lifted by bergamot and a vivid streak of limestone minerality. The palate is all silk and energy — bright citrus, lush plum and peach layered beneath a creamy, gossamer mousse, finishing with fresh hazelnut and a long, saline mineral echo. Rare, refined, and utterly unforgettable.",
        "https://www.jebsenwinesandspirits.com/cdn/shop/products/c013bol7102004-bollinger_r.d._extra_brut_1500ml.png?v=1645528920",
        "Sparkling"
    ],
    [
