        "Champagne-香檳",
        "Champagne Louis Roederer Cristal",
        "2015",
        "75cl",
        "10000.0",
        "1.0",
        "傳奇始於1876年，專為沙皇而生。2015年份Cristal以生物動力法耕作的Grand Cru葡萄園為根基，展現出令人屏息的絲滑通透。黃色水果、烘烤榛果與白花的優雅香氣引人入勝，入口後蜜餞柑橘與杏桃在舌尖輕盈綻放，白堊土的晶瑩礦感貫穿始終，尾韻純淨悠長，盡顯皇室般的高貴風範。\n\nBorn in 1876 for the Tsar of Russia, Cristal remains the ultimate symbol of Champagne royalty. The 2015 vintage, grown entirely from Louis Roederer's own biodynamic Grand Cru vineyards, is a study in purity and grace. Delicate aromas of yellow fruit, toasted hazelnut and white blossom give way to a palate of candied citrus and apricot, underpinned by a crystalline chalky minerality. Silky, vibrant and endlessly refined — this is Champagne at its most noble.",
        "https://www.my9.com.tw/cdn/shop/files/K00701-11_2000x.png?v=1709880366",
        "Sparkling"
    ],
    [
